Based on the question, "During the past 12 months, how many times has [child's name] gone to an urgent care center or clinic in a drug store or grocery store about [his/her] health? (Urgent care centers and clinics in drug stores or grocery stores are places where you do not need to make an appointment ahead of time, and do not usually see the same health care provider at each visit. This is different from a hospital emergency room.)"
